snippet.title: Swords & Souls: Neverseen Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hail, adventurer! The Neverseen beckons. Craft a new legend in this unique combat-focused RPG.

Buy it now! https://gsght.com/c/pIDee6

Now available exclusively on Kartridge, Soul Game Studios' Swords & Souls: Neverseen is the standalone follow-up to the hit web game beloved by millions. Catch pets, go fishing, play training minigames, and more as you journey across an island beset by a powerful witch!
